snippet.title: Empire of the Ants - GDC 2024 Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007652

Wishlist now on PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007652 

'Empire of the Ants' arrives in 2024 as an epic 3D Real-Time Strategy game on PlayStation 5.

French Studio Tower Five, powered by Unreal Engine 5, redefines photo-realism, offering a breathtaking journey where the smallest heroes steal the spotlight. 🐜🌟

Explore, strategize, confront and engage in diplomacy to triumph over the myriad of challenges that lie ahead. 

#ps5 #ps5games
